::Prowl::

Prowl nods, looking concerned as he steps closer to Iron Raptor.

"Ok, love, let's go to them then. But we need to get you checked out at the 
lab afterwards."

He slides a hand around her waist. "Here, lean on me. The quarters arn't too 
far."

He begins to walk toward his quarters, gently tugging her along.
